snippet.title: Did cancel culture get it wrong? Our opinions on Amber Heard and Johnny Depp.
snippet.description:
**We would like to apologize, as normally our content is available to stream as well as watch on YouTube, however we were just not happy with the audio quality of this video, and as such, decided to make this one video only. Next episode we will continue as normal as we will get that error fixed.**

Dominic and Kayla discuss their thoughts on the situation between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp and whether or not cancel culture got this one wrong.

Additionally we address movies once again going theater only, and can anything really bring down the MCU?
